===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|path}}, {{m|enm|peth}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|pæþ||path, track}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*paþaz||path}} (compare West Frisian {{m|fy|paad}}, Dutch {{m|nl|pad}}, German {{m|de|Pfad}}), Greek {{m|el|πατέω}} / {{m|el|πάτος}}, from {{etyl|xsc|en}} (compare Avestan {{m|ae|||tr=panta}}, gen. {{m|ae|||way|tr=paθa}}, Old Persian {{m|peo||tr=pathi-|sc=Xpeo}}), from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*pent-}} (compare English {{m|en|find}}). More at [[find]].

